

---- Comparison Operator -----


 == - equal to  "value should be equal, data type doesn't matter here"

 === - equal value and equal type

 != - not equal

 !== - not equal value and type

 > - greater than

 < - less than

 >= - greater than equal to

 <= - less than equal to


 -------  Logical Operators ---------


  && - and - explained as and Operator

  || - or - explained as or Operator

  ! - not - explained as not Operator

